-- BofA in talks to buy Lehman: WSJ citing source
-- 
-- Thu Sep 11, 2008 4:45pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/09/11/us-banks-lehman-talks-idUSHAR17296620080911

 

 (Reuters) - Bank of America Corp is in talks to buy Lehman Brothers, the Wall Street Journal, citing a source, said on Thursday . 

 * Declines comment on Lehman buyout talks report * WSJ citing unnamed sources, reports any Lehman deal far from certain